summary: Calista Summerstar was my answer to this winters grasp. I wanted a dark tanned female companion that looked like she spent a great deal of time in the sun, say around the Eastmarch hot springs. I met a girl at the beach a couple years ago from Rio De Janeiro Brazil who was my inspiration for this mod. There are four variants available.
